frames.caption: A lone figure stands atop a rocky outcrop, overlooking a vast, sandy landscape leading to a distant city with domed buildings and tall minarets. The sky is overcast, filled with dark clouds and a flock of birds in flight, adding to the dramatic atmosphere.
frames.description: The scene depicts a desolate, post-apocalyptic setting where a solitary person observes a cityscape characterized by grand architecture, including domes and minarets. The foreground is dominated by arid, cracked earth, suggesting a barren environment.

frames.caption: A lone figure stands atop a rocky outcrop, overlooking a vast desert cityscape. The city, with its domed buildings and minarets, stretches into the distance under a dramatic, cloudy sky. Groups of people are seen walking through the sandy streets, adding life to the ancient setting.
frames.description: The scene depicts a historical or fantastical city, possibly inspired by Middle Eastern architecture, set in a desert environment. The atmosphere is both majestic and somber, with a sense of timelessness and mystery.
